        "right_heading": "Causes of Bad Breath",
        "right_text": "<p>Everyone experiences bad breath because it’s a naturally occurring process. Our mouths can contain billions of germs, and these bacteria break down protein particles in our saliva or near our gum line. When they do, they produce foul-smelling sulfur gas, otherwise known as bad breath.</p>",
